{"tid":1788772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣思] 無可否認 運動目前正走下坡","createTime":"2019-12-19T02:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T05:55:46.000Z","uid":41993,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e60164d624bfb8a5a81b4e7c3811b8109d3dc7e","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"反送中運動已經持續左半年之久 無論係勇武衝衝子定和理非 或多或少已經有啲攰<br />\n但我地應該思考 係咪攰就乜都唔做野?<br />\n係咪無遊行 無警暴 無新嘅惡法(侮辱公職人員罪?) 就無辦法維持民氣?<br />\n咁樣對家只要唔做野我地咪散左囉?<br />\n唔應該係咁 文宣我地要照做 聲援被捕手足我地要照做<br />\n同時間 消失左好耐嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「九點/十點 吶喊」</span>我覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應該再次番黎</span><br />\n因為香港人生活節奏太快 會好易將一啲身邊發生嘅事<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">淡忘</span><br />\n尤其剛剛齊贏左區選 有一部分人會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選擇休息而沉默</span><br />\n除左各區連儂牆 Airdrop文宣之外 應該要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做多d唔同嘅野</span> <br />\n絕對唔可以對身邊發生嘅事麻木<br />\n<del>或多或少係強迫身邊人唔好忘記其他手足嘅犠牲</del><br />\n我係尼到動議<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重開「九點/十點 吶喊」 </span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-----以下開放討論-----</div>"},{"pid":"9c38082c90116a23c81c10b62a5051e3f26e37db","tid":1788772,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788d528ee595a3f4aa3e3c40ae3b610a748e7b04","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0688818b0bb5ab5c87df3f7327005ad77fd50b9","tid":1788772,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"連儂+鳩叫係基本野可以做"},{"pid":"42a353b8c4b9db6592b5c91a86de65fbeffaf80e","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0688818b0bb5ab5c87df3f7327005ad77fd50b9","tid":1788772,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"連儂+鳩叫係基本野可以做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"但係鳩叫消失左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa047d510a61402d08ccd6c83bcb6b46979a76f","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abca0c7980591663cedab6da6c6497839dc2f36d","tid":1788772,"uid":144492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"可能係節日同招拖字<br />\n但我深信無人忘記單嘢<br />\n而家係個好機會去諗下下一步<br />\n區區跑步重訓防衛術訓練<br />\n靜落嚟唔係休息唔係冷卻<br />\n係做更多準備 <br />\n當然要點防鬼都係一個concern"},{"pid":"d6ed7847f9989a8d1d3037c7779d606182a55970","tid":1788772,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"正苦好快會搞侮辱公務員罪/ 23條/ 國歌法<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9011633a4113250090b29142c2f208e47f9e556b","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abca0c7980591663cedab6da6c6497839dc2f36d","tid":1788772,"uid":144492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"可能係節日同招拖字<br />\n但我深信無人忘記單嘢<br />\n而家係個好機會去諗下下一步<br />\n區區跑步重訓防衛術訓練<br />\n靜落嚟唔係休息唔係冷卻<br />\n係做更多準備 <br />\n當然要點防鬼都係一個concern"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"節日同對家拖字訣正正係最擔心嘅野<br />\n操體能係必須的"},{"pid":"cb85b72220e7ee62e165687cca3d9f1066a9e896","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"195470846117f4f581099ee2a03bf0018dcdd473","tid":1788772,"uid":83650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d1b003aee1a5310c352d7fbbe3956c9ca95bd9c","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c868501f8b141d480a18723cce234015007254a","tid":1788772,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"